{% comment %}
  Custom template for the four Shopify policy pages
  (Shipping / Refund / Terms of Service / Privacy).

  - invicta-page-header pulls the policy title automatically when
    request.page_type == 'policy' (with breadcrumb back to Home).
  - invicta-page-content auto-renders policy.body inside the new
    typography shell when no editor blocks are configured.
  - invicta-help-cta provides a consistent "next step" footer
    pointing to Contact across every policy page.

  The .liquid form is used here because some Shopify policy
  renderers bypass JSON section templates.
{% endcomment %}

